divs: Sighting Details1. I was in the parking lot and I saw a ufo. 2. It was flashing red and blue lights. 3. I didn't know what it was but it was different. 4. It moved slow. 5. I was afraid. 6. It flew away and I didn't want to follow it in my truck because I was scared.
Summary: I saw a cigar shaped ufo flying overhead.
trends: There have been 50 other sightings in Knoxville
